text:
Request addition of following getter method to org.apache.tools.tar.TarEntry.


    /** 
     * Get this entry's link name.
     *  
     * @return This entry's link name.
     */ 
    public String getLinkName() {
        return this.linkName.toString();
    }   


Might also want to add corresponding setter method.

This would increase this package's usefulness as a stand-alone tar file
manipulation package.
